{"tid":1150803,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[重開]玩左一星期交友apps放棄/高手教路loser討論","createTime":"2019-05-12T06:32:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-17T03:16:46.000Z","uid":180913,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"e3241635c863c16591bc7998a75872f31b5c08a8","tid":1150803,"uid":180913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T06:32:05.000Z","msg":"上個post打錯太多字同未打完就post,真偽接受唔到所以再開多個.<br />\n,好多人都係死因都係無話題,上個post有user教路同Loser問題.我就放棄唔再玩交友apps(起碼要一年先可以平伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />),祝呢個Post有討論性,祝大家提防sp9公公廁/早日搵到真愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n---------<br />\n我唔知 其他人係點<br />\n我同過50幾個人傾計<br />\n咩人都有，<br />\n大陸人買身份證有<br />\n大學生有。<br />\n中5文員<br />\n公屋仔<br />\n外國回流番黎有<br />\n<br />\n我只係傾下心事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好啦<br />\n咁高學歷話自己係醫生律師big4總之條件太好個d緊係唔敢傾計唔match。<br />\n<br />\n咁咪match d毒男毒撚科<br />\n<br />\n太高質從都知我無呢個能力去駕馭到呢班人，所以一見到就飛咗去。<br />\n<br />\n咁我就選擇gov公務員中5毒撚<br />\n就算大學都選擇例如工程系多毒撚等等<br />\n<br />\n毒撚/中5/文員dead air原因<br />\n--係咁問我做緊咩我就好似<del>乞行</del>(例行)報告，佢地問我係咪同緊另一個人傾，做咩唔回佢地，<br />\n搞到好唔知想點回。<br />\n<br />\n公務員死因<br />\n----我有問佢咩興趣 中意做咩<br />\n佢話平時中意上youtube再<br />\n問咩題材佢話熱門個d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n公務員唔只係份工悶根本連人生都係<br />\n我係好 吃力不討好咁樣搵話題<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我feel到對方都係好似例行公事咁<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n黎到工程大學生（自稱工程師）<br />\n英文好，見識話題多 ，身材超正<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />j左佢d相幾次，樣就mama地（有7成似薑檸樂個樣）<br />\n本身都好地地，諗住有機會啦<br />\n我仲去過佢做既公司in過差d見過面<br />\n點知傾傾下佢send左佢訓教張相俾我我讚佢身材好，佢就叫佢奶佢。<br />\n我個時講到明我唔會做人sp純搵人吹水，<br />\n之後就急轉直下<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tWppabN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtWppabN.jpg&h=784b7c1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我決定放棄!呢年專人返工就算<br />\n-------------------<br />\n同場加映其中撚樣撚衰老9公大叔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />打擊9公,你我有責<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2FjAgci.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2FjAgci.jpg&h=4ebc2109&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9ZesRKa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9ZesRKa.jpg&h=49bd1a1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5VNYYo9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5VNYYo9.jpg&h=555c5a43&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8ca4434bc95691e8dfcc115d6807ca6cd58f3d9c","tid":1150803,"uid":41693,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T06:37:51.000Z","msg":"你本身係點一句都無提<br />\n一開始就講到自己放低身段搵毒撚<br />\n但毒撚都唔so你 講到自己好可憐<br />\n香港女仔係高貴d 但如果你下下用高姿態去搵對象 <br />\n除左自虐 我諗都好少人會理你"},{"pid":"b74a7e1b29dbd97d64f2b5df7b0fbfef37619e5a","tid":1150803,"uid":141994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T06:38:37.000Z","msg":"個阿叔真係講嘢都一陣麻甩佬味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46048e68904789b1a196f267831758306ca655b9","tid":1150803,"uid":12207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T06:41:03.000Z","msg":"唔係5星唔去<br />\n幾搞笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29ab652e003d01f4f53992931c2c4835069bdf82","tid":1150803,"uid":99836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T06:43:13.000Z","msg":"唔敢再上網識人 好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62dbc9ac18c65dbe7d33dc4951d8b22457ed416b","tid":1150803,"uid":180913,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"46048e68904789b1a196f267831758306ca65